		title <= line_text* \
	- \Spoilers
	Spoiler* $mol_expander
		label /
			<= Spoiler_label* $mol_text
				text <= spoiler_label* \
		content /
			<= Spoiler_content* $mol_text
				text <= spoiler_content* \

